WEBVTT

00:10:00.747 --> 00:10:05.123
SP: The spread of tolerance,
liberal values,

00:10:05.147 --> 00:10:07.694
respect for marginalized groups.

00:10:07.718 --> 00:10:11.474
So racism, sexism, homophobia
are all in decline.

00:10:11.498 --> 00:10:14.141
Certainly if you ask people
overtly, questions like,

00:10:14.165 --> 00:10:18.363
"Would you be upset if your child
married an African American?"

00:10:18.387 --> 00:10:21.514
"Would you move out
if an African American moved next door?"

00:10:21.538 --> 00:10:24.752
"Do you think that blacks and whites
should go to separate schools?"

00:10:24.776 --> 00:10:29.027
"Do you think that African Americans
are inherently lazier than whites?"

00:10:29.051 --> 00:10:31.241
All of them have plummeted,